commit.message:
builtins.def (BUILT_IN_ISDIGIT, [...]): Mark with ATTR_CONST_NOTHROW_LIST.

	* builtins.def (BUILT_IN_ISDIGIT, BUILT_IN_ISXDIGIT): Mark with
	ATTR_CONST_NOTHROW_LIST.

From-SVN: r80740

files.patch:

+2004-04-15  Kaveh R. Ghazi  <ghazi@caip.rutgers.edu>
+
+	* builtins.def (BUILT_IN_ISDIGIT, BUILT_IN_ISXDIGIT): Mark with
+	ATTR_CONST_NOTHROW_LIST.
